e some ppls minds about the value a bard can bring to any group... perfect group in KC has no chanter and no cleric...  Bard: Shaman: Random melee: random melee: random melee: random melee (preferably at least one warrior who can taunt when neccesary and one high dmg output monk or rogue)</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
